Render Loop:

window::start_frame()
    swapchain::aquire_image()
        <<wait for previous frame>>
        Aquire swapchain image

Record command buffer

target::submit()
    <<wait for swapchain image to be available>> (only in SwapchainVulkanRenderTarget)
    Submit Command Buffer

window::swap()
    <<wait for command buffer to finish>>
    Swap

---------------------------------------
Notes:
- image_index moved to swapchain - change to optional
- If the image_index is not set when trying to record a command buffer, throw an error

